My Professional Background

I have been in the financial planning industry since 2016. Most recently I spent four years at a smaller RIA firm where I was able to build up a strong client service team and an efficient operations/technology network. My work helped create a thriving environment for advisors to focus on business development and servicing their clients. In 2021 I joined Highland to focus in on financial planning and client service.
